						"key": "fokke",
						"displayName": "Fokke Zandbergen",
						"active": true,
						"timeZone": "Europe/Amsterdam"
					},
					"body": "This has not been removed at all and I'm not sure if we should or maybe even make it official since it's a convention used in many software to hold third party libraries injected by build tools and package managers and thus should be ignored for versioning.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/appcelerator/alloy/blob/master/Alloy/commands/compile/index.js#L189",
